longBusinessSummary: Global Poletrusion Group Corp., together with its subsidiary, Los Santos Energy Corp provides electrical distribution/transmission poles and towers for utility companies in the United States, Central America, Mexico, Canada, and internationally. It offers composite utility poles and transmission structures. The company was formerly known as Novacab International Inc. and changed its name to Global Poletrusion Group Corp. in April 2017. Global Poletrusion Group Corp. was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Miami, Florida.
